competencyQuestion: Which are the verbsenses of VerbNet?
What is the VerbClass of a verbsense?
query:
PREFIX fschema: <https://w3id.org/framester/schema/>
    PREFIX vn: <https://w3id.org/framester/vn/schema/>
    PREFIX vndata: <https://w3id.org/framester/vn/vn31/data/>
    SELECT DISTINCT ?verbClass
    WHERE{
    ?verbClass vn:containsVerbSense vndata:Choose_13050100> .
    }
    LIMIT 200
